Reviewed-by: Nithin Kumar Dabilpuram <ndabilpuram@marvell.com>
Reviewed-by: Akhil Goyal <gakhil@marvell.com>
Reviewed-by: Jerin Jacob Kollanukkaran <jerinj@marvell.com>
(cherry picked from commit c0c9c83def362f8e315666fdc536273e0f054028)
Reviewed-on: https://sj1git1.cavium.com/c/IP/SW/dataplane/dpdk/+/112106
Tested-by: Jerin Jacob Kollanukkaran <jerinj@marvell.com>
(cherry picked from commit f274542c857c65d35ad6216d4e264bb16f7ec56b)
Reviewed-on: https://sj1git1.cavium.com/c/IP/SW/dataplane/dpdk/+/118434
(cherry picked from commit 878dc1ecd54ba1ba8c2806ed493571be3b7b8402)
